[src:astemo/acura-arx-05] 48 Action Express Racing Cadillac DPi-V.R.
[src:astemo/acura-arx-05] 10 stayed a consistent threat to win races throughout the season, claiming six more podiums, including two wins at Mid-Ohio and Laguna Seca.
